    "Name": "Beowulf",
    "Details": "An advanced tech variant of the Beowulf introduced during the Jihad that has its weapon systems revised with the era's newest weaponry. The large pulse laser and one ER medium laser were dropped for a pair of medium variable speed pulse lasers in the left arm and a pair of ER small lasers, one standard small laser, and a 'Mech sword in the right arm. Triple Strength Myomer replaces the MASC to give a slightly slower, but less risky means of achieving higher speeds and deal heavier melee damage. To aid in reaching the heat levels needed for the TSM to activate, a pair of double heat sinks were removed. The Beowulf also features a C3 slave unit.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Extended Torso Twist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
